=============
NMAP Commands
=============
-sV - Version Detection
-sC - Enable Scripting Engine
-sP -PE -PA <port> <Start IP - End IP> ICMP Ping Scan
-O - Operating System
--traceroute
-P0 - Disable ICMP Pings
-sS - Perform Stealth Scanning
-n - Disable DNS Resolution
-R - Always Perform DNS Resolution
--script - Enable Scripting Engine
-sX - Christmas scan used mainly in an Linux environment
-sF - FYN scan
-sN - NULL
-sP -N - ACK scan

